    <Cell ss:StyleID="s68"><Data ss:Type="String">Please provide the following for the client to prove their source of wealth: -A CV for the client listing all companies, countries and salaries. -If the client is self employed, please provide up to date accounts, SA302's or an accountants letter completed by a suitably qualified accountant that is fully traceable online. -If the client is employed, please provide the last 3 months payslips and corresponding bank statements showing salary received. If these are unavailable, please provide bank statements for 3 months and an employers reference addressed to ORE.&#160;</Data></Cell>
