    <Cell><Data ss:Type="String">Residential</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s66"><Data ss:Type="String">The valuation will be requested on a secondhand basis excluding any new build premium with the Valuer confirming:&#160; 1. There is no oversupply of new build flats.&#160; 2. How many have already sold in the block.&#160; 3. How many flats are vacant.&#160; 4. There is no reason that all flats in the development or block won't sell.&#160; Please note that LTV may be limited or we may choose not to proceed in light of any negative comments in relation to the above.&#160;</Data></Cell>
    <Cell ss:StyleID="s66"><Data ss:Type="String">The valuation will be requested on a secondhand basis excluding any new build premium with the Valuer confirming:&#160; 1. There is no oversupply of new build flats.&#160; 2. How many have already sold in the block.&#160; 3. How many flats are vacant.&#160; 4. There is no reason that all flats in the development or block won't sell.&#160; Please note that LTV may be limited or we may choose not to proceed in light of any negative comments in relation to the above.&#160;</Data></Cell>
